## 🎯 关键发现

### ✅ 已完成的优势
1. **完整的后端基础设施**
   - Fastify + WebSocket 服务器就绪
   - 5个核心服务实现完整
   - RealtimeService 提供了完整的广播方法
   - 数据库（SQLite）已初始化

2. **完善的前端框架**
   - Vue 3 + Element Plus UI 已搭建
   - 8个页面组件已创建
   - WebSocket Store 已实现
   - 路由和状态管理完整

### 🔴 当前瓶颈（阻塞性问题）

#### 1. **AutoIterationEngine 与 Dashboard 完全未集成** 🔴 P0
- ❌ AutoIterationEngine 没有调用 Dashboard 服务
- ❌ 迭代状态不推送到 RealtimeService
- ❌ Agent 状态不推送
- ❌ 前端无法接收实时数据

#### 2. **主进程未启动 Dashboard 服务** 🔴 P0
- ❌ main.ts 没有集成 Dashboard 启动逻辑
- ❌ 无法通过 `npm start -- --auto --enable-dashboard` 启动

#### 3. **前后端数据通道未打通** 🔴 P0
- ❌ WebSocket 连接后无法接收实时数据
- ❌ Dashboard 页面显示空白或静态数据

---

## 🚀 具体开发任务清单

### 🔴 P0 任务 - 核心集成（必须立即完成）

#### **任务 0.1: AutoIterationEngine 与 Dashboard 集成** ⏱️ 1天

**问题**：AutoIterationEngine 运行时，Dashboard 无法接收实时数据

**解决方案**：修改 AutoIterationEngine，在关键节点推送状态到 Dashboard

```typescript
// 📁 文件：src/auto-iteration.ts

// 1. 导入 Dashboard 服务
import { getServices } from './dashboard/server';

export class AutoIterationEngine {
  private iterationService: any;
  private realtimeService: any;
  private dashboardServicesInitialized = false;

  // 2. 初始化 Dashboard 服务
  private initDashboardServices() {
    try {
      const services = getServices();
      this.iterationService = services.iterationService;
      this.realtimeService = services.realtimeService;
      this.dashboardServicesInitialized = true;
      console.log('✅ Dashboard 服务已连接');
    } catch (error) {
      console.warn('⚠️ Dashboard 服务未启动，跳过实时推送');
      this.dashboardServicesInitialized = false;
    }
  }

  // 3. 在 runIteration() 开始时推送
  async runIteration() {
    // 初始化服务（如果还未初始化）
    if (!this.dashboardServicesInitialized) {
      this.initDashboardServices();
    }

    console.log(`\n${'='.repeat(60)}`);
    console.log(`🔄 迭代 #${this.iterationCount}`);
    console.log(`${'='.repeat(60)}`);

    // 创建迭代记录
    let iterationId: string | null = null;
    if (this.dashboardServicesInitialized) {
      try {
        const iteration = await this.iterationService.create({
          iterationNumber: this.iterationCount,
          status: 'running',
          requirement: '自动迭代任务',
          createdAt: new Date()
        });
        iterationId = iteration.id;

        // 推送迭代状态
        this.realtimeService.broadcastIterationStatusChange({
          id: iteration.id,
          iterationNumber: this.iterationCount,
          status: 'running',
          progress: 0,
          requirement: '自动迭代任务'
        });
      } catch (error) {
        console.error('创建迭代记录失败:', error);
      }
    }

    try {
      // 产品经理分析需求
      await this.runPhase('product-manager', this.productManager, iterationId);

      // 执行各 Agent
      await this.runPhase('architect', this.agents.architect, iterationId);
      await this.runPhase('database', this.agents.database, iterationId);
      await this.runPhase('backend', this.agents.backend, iterationId);
      await this.runPhase('frontend', this.agents.frontend, iterationId);
      await this.runPhase('ui-designer', this.agents.uiDesigner, iterationId);
      await this.runPhase('tester', this.agents.tester, iterationId);
      await this.runPhase('security', this.agents.security, iterationId);
      await this.runPhase('documenter', this.agents.documenter, iterationId);
      await this.runPhase('assets', this.agents.assets, iterationId);

      // Git 提交
      const commitResult = await this.gitCommit();

      // 完成迭代
      if (this.dashboardServicesInitialized && iterationId) {
        await this.iterationService.update(iterationId, {
          status: 'success',
          progress: 100,
          completedAt: new Date()
        });

        this.realtimeService.broadcastIterationStatusChange({
          id: iterationId,
          iterationNumber: this.iterationCount,
          status: 'success',
          progress: 100
        });
      }

      this.history.push({
        iteration: this.iterationCount,
        task: 'auto-iteration',
        status: 'success',
        message: '迭代成功完成',
        timestamp: new Date()
      });

    } catch (error) {
      console.error('❌ 迭代失败:', error);

      if (this.dashboardServicesInitialized && iterationId) {
        await this.iterationService.update(iterationId, {
          status: 'failed',
          errorMessage: String(error)
        });

        this.realtimeService.broadcastIterationStatusChange({
          id: iterationId,
          iterationNumber: this.iterationCount,
          status: 'failed',
          errorMessage: String(error)
        });
      }

      this.history.push({
        iteration: this.iterationCount,
        task: 'auto-iteration',
        status: 'failed',
        message: String(error),
        timestamp: new Date()
      });
    }
  }

  // 4. 执行 Agent 阶段
  private async runPhase(
    phaseName: string, 
    agent: BaseAgent, 
    iterationId: string | null
  ) {
    console.log(`\n🎯 执行 ${phaseName}...`);

    // 推送 Agent 状态开始
    if (this.dashboardServicesInitialized && iterationId) {
      this.realtimeService.broadcastAgentStatusChange({
        name: phaseName,
        displayName: agent.displayName || phaseName,
        status: 'running',
        iterationId,
        currentTask: `${phaseName} 进行中...`,
        progress: 0
      });
    }

    const startTime = Date.now();
    try {
      const result = await agent.execute(this.currentRequirement || '自动迭代');
      const duration = Date.now() - startTime;

      console.log(`✅ ${phaseName} 完成 (${duration}ms)`);

      // 推送 Agent 状态完成
      if (this.dashboardServicesInitialized && iterationId) {
        this.realtimeService.broadcastAgentStatusChange({
          name: phaseName,
          displayName: agent.displayName || phaseName,
          status: 'success',
          iterationId,
          currentTask: `${phaseName} 已完成`,
          progress: 100,
          duration
        });

        // 更新迭代进度
        const progress = this.calculateProgress(phaseName);
        this.realtimeService.broadcastIterationProgress({
          id: iterationId,
          progress
        });
      }

      return result;
    } catch (error) {
      const duration = Date.now() - startTime;
      console.error(`❌ ${phaseName} 失败:`, error);

      // 推送 Agent 状态失败
      if (this.dashboardServicesInitialized && iterationId) {
        this.realtimeService.broadcastAgentStatusChange({
          name: phaseName,
          displayName: agent.displayName || phaseName,
          status: 'failed',
          iterationId,
          currentTask: `${phaseName} 失败`,
          progress: 0,
          duration,
          errorMessage: String(error)
        });
      }

      throw error;
    }
  }

  // 5. 计算进度
  private calculateProgress(currentPhase: string): number {
    const phases = [
      'product-manager', 'architect', 'database', 'backend',
      'frontend', 'ui-designer', 'tester', 'security',
      'documenter', 'assets'
    ];
    const currentIndex = phases.indexOf(currentPhase);
    return Math.floor(((currentIndex + 1) / phases.length) * 100);
  }

  // 6. Git 提交
  private async gitCommit() {
    // ... 现有 Git 提交逻辑
  }
}
```

**验收标准**：
- ✅ AutoIterationEngine 启动时自动连接 Dashboard 服务
- ✅ 迭代开始时推送状态到 WebSocket
- ✅ 每个 Agent 执行时推送状态更新
- ✅ 迭代完成时推送最终状态
- ✅ Dashboard 前端能实时看到迭代进度

